<div class="col-sm-2"><i class="fa fa-briefcase fa-2x"></i></div><h3>ABOUT THE SILICON VALLEY BRIEFING</h3>

  In 2014, our inaugural Silicon Valley Briefing welcomed 45 Consuls from 34 countries to the Stanford Faculty Club for a briefing by executives, entrepreneurs, venture capitalists and thought leaders from Silicon Valley. Based on extraordinary participation and requests for annual events from many Consuls General, the Association hosted a briefing at the Computer History Museum in 2015. The Association is pleased offer the 2016 Silicon Valley Briefing at the Mission Bay Conference Center at the University of California, San Francisco.
